# <!-- REQUIRED -->
# Mandatory Audit (Always Active)

## After Every Phase Completion

Run the appropriate quality gate phase:

```bash
# After implementation work
bash scripts/gate-runner.sh wo_exit --continue-on-failure

# Before any commit
bash scripts/gate-runner.sh pre_commit --continue-on-failure
```

## Audit Results

- **Blocking failures** (tier 0-1): Must be resolved before proceeding
- **Advisory failures** (tier 2-3): Document in WO, resolve when practical
- **Baselined failures**: Pre-existing issues tracked in manifest, not regressions

## No Silent Failures

- Every gate run must be acknowledged
- Failed gates must have a resolution path documented
- Do not suppress or ignore gate output
